457
00:43:14,640 --> 00:43:18,300
He couldn't even protect those he trusted the most.

458
00:43:21,320 --> 00:43:25,560
Enough. It's enough now.

459
00:43:27,660 --> 00:43:31,750
Since you're so determined, I won't force you to stay.

460
00:43:35,140 --> 00:43:37,330
Your Imperial Highness, may I ask you

461
00:43:38,490 --> 00:43:41,160
