462
00:43:42,940 --> 00:43:46,070
She chose her own road.

463
00:43:46,070 --> 00:43:48,720
There's nothing more I can say to convince her otherwise.

464
00:43:50,620 --> 00:43:52,590
Just tell her to be cautious

465
00:43:53,290 --> 00:43:55,150
